Homepage: https://github.com/seanchatmangpt/ggen
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: ggen
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: deterministic, language-agnostic code generation from RDF
 ggen is a deterministic, language-agnostic code generation framework
 that treats software artifacts as projections of knowledge graphs.
 .
 This package ships the prebuilt `ggen` CLI binary. The Rust source
 build itself happens before packaging (see debian/rules); this
 package's own build step only stages the already-compiled binary.
